1. **Architecture/data flow update** (if the pipeline changed)
2. **List of defects/gaps found** and how you fixed each
3. **Updated code** in repo(s) with clear commits
4. **Tests** (unit tests for data mapping + packet logic where possible)
5. **Logging and retry strategy** documentation
6. **"How to verify"** checklist (step-by-step)

---

## Inputs Available (assume they exist)

- SignNow credentials (API key / OAuth client) — in GAS Script Properties + Netlify env vars
- Google service account with Drive + Sheets permissions — GAS native auth
- PDF templates — in Google Drive, referenced by template IDs in [PDF_Mappings.js](file:///Users/brendan/Desktop/shamrock-bail-portal-site/backend-gas/PDF_Mappings.js)
- Telegram Bot Token — in GAS Script Properties + Netlify env vars
- ElevenLabs API Key + Agent ID — in Netlify env vars + GAS Script Properties
- Twilio credentials — in GAS Script Properties + Netlify env vars
- Example intake payloads — available via [Test_Suite.js](file:///Users/brendan/Desktop/shamrock-bail-portal-site/backend-gas/Test_Suite.js), [Test_Integrations.js](file:///Users/brendan/Desktop/shamrock-bail-portal-site/backend-gas/Test_Integrations.js), [Test_PDF_Hydration.js](file:///Users/brendan/Desktop/shamrock-bail-portal-site/backend-gas/Test_PDF_Hydration.js) in GAS

If any credential is missing from a given platform, create a placeholder and clearly document what's needed.

